modName: Women's Faces NPS - English- Missing Name Patch
summary: This small esp patch is an attempt to fix the infamous missing npc names in Women's Faces mod.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]Description:[/size]
One of my favorite NPC overhaul mod is Women's Faces by veter75n here on Nexus. Unfortunately, it suffered missing NPC names resulting in unlootable NPCs. This simple patch fixes that problem.

Requirement:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59133/?]Women's Faces by veter75n[/url]

Installation: 
1. Install Women's Faces
2. Install this patch

Version:
1.6- Fixes Women's faces 1.6
author: 00m9
